{"thig13.3:0.1":"Therigatha 13.3 ","thig13.3:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thig13.3:0.3":"Capatherigatha ","thig13.3:1.1":"“Latthihattho pure asi, ","thig13.3:1.2":"so dani migaluddako; ","thig13.3:1.3":"Asaya palipa ghora, ","thig13.3:1.4":"nasakkhi parametave. ","thig13.3:2.1":"Sumattam mam mannamana, ","thig13.3:2.2":"capa puttamatosayi; ","thig13.3:2.3":"Capaya bandhanam chetva, ","thig13.3:2.4":"pabbajissam punopaham”. ","thig13.3:3.1":"“Ma me kujjhi mahavira, ","thig13.3:3.2":"ma me kujjhi mahamuni; ","thig13.3:3.3":"Na hi kodhaparetassa, ","thig13.3:3.4":"suddhi atthi kuto tapo”. ","thig13.3:4.1":"“Pakkamissanca nalato, ","thig13.3:4.2":"kodha nalaya vacchati; ","thig13.3:4.3":"Bandhanti itthirupena, ","thig13.3:4.4":"samane dhammajivino”. ","thig13.3:5.1":"“Ehi kala nivattassu, ","thig13.3:5.2":"bhunja kame yatha pure; ","thig13.3:5.3":"Ahanca te vasikata, ","thig13.3:5.4":"ye ca me santi nataka”. ","thig13.3:6.1":"“Etto cape catubbhagam, ","thig13.3:6.2":"yatha bhasasi tvanca me; ","thig13.3:6.3":"Tayi rattassa posassa, ","thig13.3:6.4":"ularam vata tam siya”. ","thig13.3:7.1":"“Kalanginimva takkarim, ","thig13.3:7.2":"pupphitam girimuddhani; ","thig13.3:7.3":"Phullam dalimalatthimva, ","thig13.3:7.4":"antodipeva patalim. ","thig13.3:8.1":"Haricandanalittangim, ","thig13.3:8.2":"kasikuttamadharinim; ","thig13.3:8.3":"Tam mam rupavatim santim, ","thig13.3:8.4":"kassa ohaya gacchasi”. ","thig13.3:9.1":"“Sakuntikova sakunim, ","thig13.3:9.2":"yatha bandhitumicchati; ","thig13.3:9.3":"Aharimena rupena, ","thig13.3:9.4":"na mam tvam badhayissasi”. ","thig13.3:10.1":"“Imanca me puttaphalam, ","thig13.3:10.2":"kala uppaditam taya; ","thig13.3:10.3":"Tam mam puttavatim santim, ","thig13.3:10.4":"kassa ohaya gacchasi”. ","thig13.3:11.1":"“Jahanti putte sappanna, ","thig13.3:11.2":"tato nati tato dhanam; ","thig13.3:11.3":"Pabbajanti mahavira, ","thig13.3:11.4":"nago chetvava bandhanam”. ","thig13.3:12.1":"“Idani te imam puttam, ","thig13.3:12.2":"Dandena churikaya va; ","thig13.3:12.3":"Bhumiyam va nisumbhissam, ","thig13.3:12.4":"Puttasoka na gacchasi”. ","thig13.3:13.1":"“Sace puttam singalanam, ","thig13.3:13.2":"kukkuranam padahisi; ","thig13.3:13.3":"Na mam puttakatte jammi, ","thig13.3:13.4":"punaravattayissasi”. ","thig13.3:14.1":"“Handa kho dani bhaddante, ","thig13.3:14.2":"kuhim kala gamissasi; ","thig13.3:14.3":"Katamam gamanigamam, ","thig13.3:14.4":"nagaram rajadhaniyo”. ","thig13.3:15.1":"“Ahumha pubbe ganino, ","thig13.3:15.2":"Assamana samanamanino; ","thig13.3:15.3":"Gamena gamam vicarimha, ","thig13.3:15.4":"Nagare rajadhaniyo. ","thig13.3:16.1":"Eso hi bhagava buddho, ","thig13.3:16.2":"nadim neranjaram pati; ","thig13.3:16.3":"Sabbadukkhappahanaya, ","thig13.3:16.4":"dhammam deseti paninam; ","thig13.3:16.5":"Tassaham santikam gaccham, ","thig13.3:16.6":"so me sattha bhavissati”. ","thig13.3:17.1":"“Vandanam dani vajjasi, ","thig13.3:17.2":"lokanatham anuttaram; ","thig13.3:17.3":"Padakkhinanca katvana, ","thig13.3:17.4":"adiseyyasi dakkhinam”. ","thig13.3:18.1":"“Etam kho labbhamamhehi, ","thig13.3:18.2":"yatha bhasasi tvanca me; ","thig13.3:18.3":"Vandanam dani te vajjam, ","thig13.3:18.4":"lokanatham anuttaram; ","thig13.3:18.5":"Padakkhinanca katvana, ","thig13.3:18.6":"adisissami dakkhinam”. ","thig13.3:19.1":"Tato ca kalo pakkami, ","thig13.3:19.2":"nadim neranjaram pati; ","thig13.3:19.3":"So addasasi sambuddham, ","thig13.3:19.4":"desentam amatam padam. ","thig13.3:20.1":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","thig13.3:20.2":"dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","thig13.3:20.3":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","thig13.3:20.4":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","thig13.3:21.1":"Tassa padani vanditva, ","thig13.3:21.2":"Katvana nam padakkhinam; ","thig13.3:21.3":"Capaya adisitvana, ","thig13.3:21.4":"Pabbajim anagariyam; ","thig13.3:21.5":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig13.3:21.6":"Katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig13.3:22.1":"… Capa theri …. "}